+/*
+ * Analog Front End (AFE), per RF core.
+ *
+ * Offsets extracted by static analysis of wlc_phy_radio2069_afecal
+ * (@0x3a908). The function modifies reg 0x725 with mask 0x4 and reg
+ * 0x739 with mask 0x80 on core 0, plus the same offset pattern at
+ * +0x200 stride for upper cores. The mask-0x4 register is the AFE
